refsection.programlisting:
r1=tvp('con','inc','cte','R=sigu','Q=0.1*eye(2,2)','priorb0=b','priorv0=100000*eye(2,2)','tvpmeth=1')
// Example taken from function tvp_d1.
// Here the variance of the innovations of the time varying coefficients is assumed to be diagonal
// and there is a diffuse prior for starting values (tvpmeth=1);
// endogenous variable is 'con', the exogenous ones are'inc' and 'cte';
// starting values are given for R, Q and priorb0; priorv0 is imposed.
